The first undoubted issue of the provisional government came out in March. The set of eight, with values ranging from one lepton to 5 drachma, all depicted an infantryman aiming a rifle while others look on; the frames of the 10l and 25l values are inscribed only with ". Instead of being perforated, they have a serrate roulette that superficially resembles perforation, but is distinguished by angled cuts 
rather than the round roles of perforation.

